#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:2
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Mulai cepat"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:4
msgid "Get up and running with django-hstore-project in under a minute."
msgstr "Mulai dengan django-hstore-project dalam kurang dari satu menit."

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:7
msgid "Create a Model"
msgstr "Buat model"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:9
msgid "Add an HStore field to any model:"
msgstr "Tambahkan field HStore ke model apa pun:"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:21
msgid "That's it. The widget is auto-wired, no form configuration needed."
msgstr "Selesai. Widget auto-wired, tidak perlu konfigurasi formulir."

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:24
msgid "Run Migrations"
msgstr "Jalankan migrasi"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:31
msgid "This enables the PostgreSQL hstore extension automatically."
msgstr "Ini mengaktifkan ekstensi hstore PostgreSQL secara otomatis."

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:34
msgid "Register in Admin"
msgstr "Daftar di Admin"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:46
msgid ""
"Visit your admin page and you'll see the HStore widget with a clean key-"
"value interface. Each key-value pair is editable inline. Add, remove, and "
"modify pairs as needed."
msgstr ""
"Kunjungi halaman admin Anda dan Anda akan melihat widget HStore dengan "
"antarmuka key-value yang bersih. Setiap pasangan key-value dapat diedit "
"inline. Tambah, hapus, dan modifikasi pasangan sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:51
msgid "With Custom Keys"
msgstr "Dengan kunci kustom"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:53
msgid ""
"Define explicit keys to get labeled form fields instead of the free-form "
"editor:"
msgstr ""
"Definisikan kunci eksplisit untuk mendapatkan field formulir berlabel bukan "
"editor bebas:"

#: ../../docs/user-guide/quickstart.rst:70
msgid ""
"Each key becomes a proper form field with validation, widgets, and labels."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kunci menjadi field formulir yang tepat dengan validasi, widget, dan "
"label."

